CODParameter.name: file
CODParameter.Definition: The file parameter is the primary key, i.e. the unique number, defining a crystal saved in the COD database.

CODParameter.name: a
CODParameter.Definition: The lattice parameter a of the crysatl structure.

CODParameter.name: siga
CODParameter.Definition: The standard deviation of the lattice parameter a of the crysatl structure.

CODParameter.name: b
CODParameter.Definition: The lattice parameter b of the crysatl structure.

CODParameter.name: sigb
CODParameter.Definition: The standard deviation of the lattice parameter b of the crysatl structure.

CODParameter.name: c
CODParameter.Definition: The lattice parameter c of the crysatl structure.

CODParameter.name: sigc
CODParameter.Definition: The standard deviation of the lattice parameter c of the crysatl structure.

CODParameter.name: alpha
CODParameter.Definition: The lattice parameter alpha of the crysatl structure.

CODParameter.name: sigalpha
CODParameter.Definition: The standard deviation of the lattice parameter alpha of the crysatl structure.

CODParameter.name: beta
CODParameter.Definition: The lattice parameter beta of the crysatl structure.

CODParameter.name: sigbeta
CODParameter.Definition: The standard deviation of the lattice parameter beta of the crysatl structure.

CODParameter.name: gamma
CODParameter.Definition: The lattice parameter gamma of the crysatl structure.

CODParameter.name: siggamma
CODParameter.Definition: The standard deviation of the lattice parameter gamma of the crysatl structure.

CODParameter.name: vol
CODParameter.Definition: The volume of the crysatl structure.

CODParameter.name: sigvol
CODParameter.Definition: The standard deviation of the volume of the crysatl structure.

CODParameter.name: celltemp
CODParameter.Definition: The temperature at which the crystal structure was determined.

CODParameter.name: sigcelltemp
CODParameter.Definition: The standard deviation of the temperature at which the crystal structure was determined.

CODParameter.name: sigvol
CODParameter.Definition: The standard deviation of the temperature at which the crystal structure was determined.

CODParameter.name: cellpressure
CODParameter.Definition: The cell pressure at which the crystal structure was determined.

CODParameter.name: sigcellpressure
CODParameter.Definition: The standard deviation of the cell pressure at which the crystal structure was determined.

CODParameter.name: thermalhist
CODParameter.Definition: The thermal history of the crystal.

CODParameter.name: pressurehist
CODParameter.Definition: The pressure history of the crystal.

CODParameter.name: nel
CODParameter.Definition: The Neel temperature of the crystal.

CODParameter.name: commonname
CODParameter.Definition: The common name of the cyrstal.

CODParameter.name: chemname
CODParameter.Definition: The chemical name of the crystal.

CODParameter.name: mineral
CODParameter.Definition: The mineral the crystal belongs to.

CODParameter.name: formula
CODParameter.Definition: The formula that describes the crystal.

CODParameter.name: calcformula
CODParameter.Definition: The calculated formula that describes the crystal.

CODParameter.name: authors
CODParameter.Definition: The authors that published the CIF file describing the crystal in the COD database.

CODParameter.name: title
CODParameter.Definition: The title of the scientific paper where the crystal structure was published.

CODParameter.name: journal
CODParameter.Definition: The name of the scientific paper where the crystal structure was published.

CODParameter.name: year
CODParameter.Definition: The year of publication of this crystal structure.

CODParameter.name: volume
CODParameter.Definition: The volume of the scientific paper where the crystal structure was published.

CODParameter.name: issue
CODParameter.Definition: The issue of the scientific paper where the crystal structure was published.

CODParameter.name: firstpage
CODParameter.Definition: The first page of the scientific paper where the crystal structure was published.

CODParameter.name: lastpage
CODParameter.Definition: The last page of the scientific paper where the crystal structure was published.

CODParameter.name: doi
CODParameter.Definition: The DOI that links to the online paper where the cyrstal was published.

CODParameter.name: method
CODParameter.Definition: The method that was used to determine the crystal structure.

CODParameter.name: radiation
CODParameter.Definition: The radiation that was used to determine the crystal structure.

CODParameter.name: wavelength
CODParameter.Definition: The wavelength that was used to determine the crystal structure.

CODParameter.name: date
CODParameter.Definition: The date the crystal structure was published to COD database.

CODParameter.name: time
CODParameter.Definition: The time the crystal structure was published to COD database.
